Cottage Septic & Plumbing Services Inc. is company owned and operated. We proudly serve Muskoka, Parry Sound, Bracebridge, Gravenhurst, Huntsville, Dorset, Dwight and Lake of Bays. Our licensed professionals are dedicated to going above and beyond when it comes to septic systems, excavation and plumbing. Our mission is to provide the best quality workmanship, stress-free and relaxed environment for our clients.

Licensed & insured!

profile:
Our family-owned and operated company Cottage Country Stone Ltd. specializes in:
- complete septic systems
- lot clearing
- tree removal
- driveways
- hard landscaping
- waterproofing
- stone installation 
- flat concrete work
- home renovation
- wooden fences
 
We are proud to provide excellent customer service to our clients for over 20 years.  
For any of your projects, we would be happy to give you a free estimate. It doesn't matter if your project is big or small.
​
See our galleries and services at our website; www.cottagecountrystone.com
We are comfortable just help people to find the best solution, give the estimate and do what we promise to do!
 
As you go through our website you can see a variety of the services we provide to our clients.
